  "text": "Among other techniques we mention the relevant ones and indicate the review works done in this direction next. Raja and Bhaskaran [CITATION_1] proposed a new technique called population reduction (PR) in their study. Population reduction applies tournament selection after dividing the initial population into groups to select the best fit candidates. After that, the selected best fit individuals are entered to simple GA. This technique has been carried out on 0/1 knapsack problem to study the impact of multi variables as follows:",
